text: I've always wanted to have sex with this cute office lady... but when I took her home... she was an extremely virile woman... and we did it, and did it, and she did it over and over again. "You wanted to have sex, didn't you? With me..." "I'll do it until you use up all the condoms lol" My simple ulterior motives backfired unexpectedly!? The sexual desire of a working woman is unrivaled! "I want to cum more!!" I never thought I'd end up having sex this much... This is an incredible night... we did it, and did it, and did it!!
trans: J'ai toujours voulu faire l'amour avec cette jolie femme de bureau... mais quand je l'ai ramenée chez moi... c'était une femme extrêmement virile... et nous l'avons fait, et fait, et elle l'a fait encore et encore. « Tu voulais faire l'amour, n'est-ce pas ?
